Technosfera-mail.ru - Information Retrival - Final Project

simple start:
	1) create your environment: virtualenv <ENV_NAME>
	2) activate it:             source <ENV_NAME>/bin/activate
	3) install requirements:    pip install -r requirements.txt
        4) run init.sh              ./init.sh
        5) run django project:      ./manage.py runserver
        6) open in browser:         http://127.0.0.1:8000

lyrics
	it is main application of django project
       

collect_data
	contain scripts for collect_dataing data using VK API

        Firstly, you should set your VK id and token in collect_data/get_songs.py
        collect_data/get_songs.py  - extract songs, which have lyrics, to songs.csv using VK API
        collect_data/read_songs.py - example of reading songs.csv file
        collect_data/wordlist.py   - contain list with russian words
